######################################################################################################
 # Updates :
 # Date       |Author   |Version|Description
 # 2016-02-17 |Bader    |U10_02 |Bugfixing
 # 2016-02-19 |DNE      |U10    |Bugfixing (SAM #114567)
 # 2016-02-22 |Bader    |U10    |SAM #114656: OK_BVR_BIS: Call LEC_TPV_LEG instead of direct reading in [F:TPV]
 # 2016-03-08 |ANGRE    |U10    |SAM #115076: OK_BVR_BIS: Removed the branch for existing invoices.
 # 2018-05.28 |Bader    |2018.R5|SET_AMOUNT_BIS: Call AFFCOL only if amount has changed
